It's not a deal.

255
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:20,630
是机遇
It's an opportunity.

256
00:11:22,140 --> 00:11:23,510
算了吧
I'll be just fine.

257
00:11:26,300 --> 00:11:28,270
你或许鄙视我  奥林
You may despise me, Orrin,

258
00:11:28,280 --> 00:11:29,680
