Doug, check with Linda.

275
00:12:58,540 --> 00:12:59,680
这就去
Calling her now.

276
00:13:00,550 --> 00:13:04,890
好的  现在可以谈谈特许学校了吗
Okay, so now can we talk about charter schools?

277
00:13:04,890 --> 00:13:06,230
