Charter schools are a no-go.

278
00:13:06,230 --> 00:13:07,310
法案里必须有
They have to be in there.

279
00:13:07,310 --> 00:13:08,510
保留他们  就别谈了
You keep them in, we walk.

280
00:13:08,510 --> 00:13:09,550
我们也是
The same goes for us.

281
00:13:09,550 --> 00:13:10,920
别急着下最后通牒
Let's not jump to ultimatums.

282
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:13,910
想办法减少对非公立学校的资助吧
Well, let's figure out a way to reduce non-public spending.

283
00:13:14,560 --> 00:13:16,370
